<ContentLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How the Salafi Science Network handles visitor data and respects user privacy."
  category="Policy"
  updated="November 2024"
>
  <p>
    We operate the Salafi Science Network as a static educational resource. We do not track individual users or sell any
    personal information. Any analytics tools employed are anonymised and only used to improve content delivery.
  </p>
  <h2>Information collection</h2>
  <p>
    The site stores only essential technical data in temporary server logs such as IP address, browser type, and page
    visited. This information is automatically purged and never shared with third parties.
  </p>
  <h2>Contact forms</h2>
  <p>
    When you contact us via email, we only retain the details required to respond to your request. Messages are stored
    securely and removed once the correspondence is complete.
  </p>
  <h2>External links</h2>
  <p>
    Some pages may link to external resources. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these
    websites, and we advise visitors to review their respective policies.
  </p>
  <p>
    For any concerns regarding privacy, please email
    <a href="mailto:privacy@salafisciencenetwork.org">privacy@salafisciencenetwork.org</a>.
  </p>
</ContentLayout>
